title: Slayer - When The Stillness Comes (2 trks) 2015 a4k
description:
I thought about this and almost gave a thumbs down.
 But It was the second track that was originally meant to accompany the single. 
So here it is, wish I would have been able to score them at same time but It is what it is......and that's still SLAYER 

1 When The Stillness Come
2. Black Magic (Live at Wacken)



Still wish I had scored both at same time
